{"tid":430942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你講雙十節會激嬲中共唔代表你係中華民國人","createTime":"2017-10-10T08:56:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T09:26:30.000Z","uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ba048df7cccb37c7d38d87db766a316952cbee87","tid":430942,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T08:56:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.ytimg.com/vi/jhwHR0TVBk4/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FjhwHR0TVBk4%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=bbbca484&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要排排國慶，開埠、queen&rsquo;s birthday 係國慶都未到雙十啦<br />\n雙十只係堆支那人（中華民國先係支那正宗）落香港，英國收留你地，但仲要插外國國旗，慶外國國慶嘅垃圾咋"},{"pid":"4c8ec31bf5b83badc5b1fd9b86da34e0e8c1ae12","tid":430942,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T09:01:28.000Z","msg":"雙十節本身就係吹捧嗰個偷渡去人地國家，雀巢鳩佔，自己圍爐慶自己國家國慶嘅文化<br />\n放返現代，等同中國人去英國，之後係大街小巷掛晒中共旗慶祝中國國慶，之後每年就同英國人講，「今日就係英國嘅國慶啦！」一樣"},{"pid":"2072b0f5d180c537697bc0d9d4d5bd5c3c785366","tid":430942,"uid":3295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T09:26:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雙十節本身就係吹捧嗰個偷渡去人地國家，雀巢鳩佔，自己圍爐慶自己國家國慶嘅文化<br />\n放返現代，等同中國人去英國，之後係大街小巷掛晒中共旗慶祝中國國慶，之後每年就同英國人講，「今日就係英國嘅國慶啦！」一樣</blockquote><br />\n偷渡好似淡化左個情況<br />\n分明係入城種族屠殺"}]}